(Maachị 11, 1890 ruo Nọvemba 29, 1968) bụ onye Amerịka na-ese ụkpụrụ ụlọ. Onye Afrịka Amerịka, a na-eto ya maka imepụta Mahadum Virginia nke Lynchburg (nke mbụ bụ Lynchburg Baptist Seminary) na Lynchburg, Virginia na Saint Paul African Union Methodist Church na Washington D.C
A na-edepụta ha abụọ na National Register of Historic Places.
A mụrụ ya na Norfolk, Virginia. Nna ya bụ Romulus Cornelius Archer na nne ya Mary Poindexter Archer. Ọ lụrụ onye nkuzi na onye isi ikike obodo bụ Louise Archer.
Architect James Alonzo Plater malitere ọrụ ya na-arụ ọrụ maka Archer site na 1934 ruo 1936 tupu ọ kwaga Philadelphia. Onye na-ese ụkpụrụ ụlọ bụ John B

(1913 ruo 1983) rụrụ ọrụ maka ya obere oge n'ihe dị ka 1938. Holloway na Archer mepụtara ebe obibi na Eastland Gardens.
E gosipụtara Archer na Jet na foto mgbe ọ nwetasịrị ihe nrite site na Washington Board of Trade.
Ọrụ Archer gụnyere ebe obibi, ụlọ ahịa, ụlọ obibi na ụlọ ụka dị n'ebe ugwu ọwụwa anyanwụ Brookland nke Washington DC.
E liri ya na Arlington National Cemetery.
